     <tr><td><Script>document.title = "Illia's Everquest Bestiary: Inferno Goblin Wizard";</script>
	   <table width="100%" border=0><tr><td valign=top><h2 style='font-size:22px;'>
	   Inferno Goblin Wizard
	   </h2></td></tr>
	   <tr><td><em>Monster</em></td></tr>
	   <tr><td valign=top "width=100%"><p>Inferno Goblins are second to Solusek goblins in difficulty.  They are found throughout Solusek's Eye, and are typically encountered around the bar area of the Castle.<br><br>The wizards can be paritularily dangerous, and despite their low HPs, can cause significant amounts of damage in a short time.<br><br>Like all casters in Solusek's Eye, the Wizards can see invisible.<br></p></td></tr>
	   <tr><td valign=top><b>Minimum Level</b>: 26 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b>Maximum Level</b>: 27 </td></tr><tr><td valign=top><b>Known Loot:</b><li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=14519">Fiery Ore</a></li>
<li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=2900">Heart of Fire</a></li>
<li><a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=6066">Pouch of Red Dust</a></li>
